9mobile now has a simple, easy and convenient multipurpose short code *996# to verify and link
customers’ National Identification Number (NIN) to their mobile number(s)-You can link up all your 
mobile numbers with one NIN. What’s more, you can also get information about NIN Registration
centres across Nigeria right on your phone
3 simple steps
Dial *996# and 1. Dial 1 to confirm if your NIN has been successfully linked to your phone number 2. Dial 2 to link your 11-digit NIN 3. Dial 3 to get information about NIN Registration centers across Nigeria
Subscribers can also verify and link their NIN to their mobile number(s) online using the
link https://9mobile.com.ng/nin
It’s that simple
